# Coffee Rating Application ☕

A Flask-based web application where users can vote for their favorite coffee items.

## Features

- Display coffee list
- Coffee images
- Vote button functionality
- Database vote storage
- Dynamic vote updates
- Flask backend integration

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML
- CSS

## Project Structure

coffee-rating-app/
│
├── app.py
├── templates/
│ └── index.html
├── static/
│ ├── style.css
│ └── images/

## How to Run

1. Install Flask

```bash
py -m pip install flask
```

2. Run application

```bash
py app.py
```

3. Open browser

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

